+  # interactive_claude_wrapper.sh (invoked by ClaudeLauncher) and
+  # stop_hook.sh (invoked by StopHookInstaller). `bash <missing-file>`
+  # exited instantly and killed the tmux session before Hive could
+  # inspect it; the missing stop hook meant .done / result.json were
+  # never written. These tests guard the packaging fix end-to-end.
