+  # every script referenced by ClaudeLauncher / StopHookInstaller is inside
+  # the packaged artifact, AND that the packaged script set equals the
+  # on-disk set (a script added to disk but not to the gemspec fails loudly,
+  # future-proofing beyond the two known references). Skips with a clear
+  # message if the rubygems build toolchain is unavailable so minimal dev
+  # environments are not broken while CI still runs the full guard.
